<br>
<br>
I need any info that can be given for guilds that are accepting members on Stormhammer. I was recently on the Seventh Hammer server, but moved to Stormhammer to find something better. Since PoP it has been hard to find any decent Guilds that do not require 3 months of devoted time just to get to an approval to go to a vote of yea or nay or a minimum level of 60. Also, those that are active and at least somewhat knowledgeable. I do not mind putting time and effort into a guild, but do to work there are times when I may not be able to attend the weekly and sometimes daily raid. Any info would be appreciated.<br>
